<Layout title="Is a Higher Salary Always Better? The Total Compensation Equation | Econified" description="Learn why base salary is only 60-80% of your total compensation and how to calculate the real value of benefits, PTO, and retirement matching." canonicalUrl="https://econified.com/guides/total-compensation-equation/">
  <main class="container" style="max-width: 780px;">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
